    "We did not study the sensitivity of the resulting mesh to the weighting factor, but we assume its influence to be minor.",
    "The region of interest for the analysis was reduced to Reducing the grid size enabled the SVD computation using the volume data, which is not feasible for the original data without a dedicated distributed-memory parallel algorithm.",
    "Hence, only SVD results obtained on the reduced data are presented.",
    "Due to the large number of cells generated, this test case could not be executed on a local machine.",
    "Instead, both the grid generation and SVD were performed on an HPC cluster using 128 CPU cores."
